# Implementation Plan V2 - Direct Response Funnel

## Goal Description
Pivot the Wishtune implementation from a standard e-commerce site to a **Direct Response Funnel** based on the "Free Manifestation Song" lead magnet found on `riagupta.com`.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Major Strategy Change**:
> - We are hiding the "Shop" initially.
> - **Primary Landing Page** will now be a **Squeeze Page** (Email Capture for Free Song).
> - **After Submit**, user is redirected to a **Best Seller One-Time Offer (OTO)** page.

## Proposed Changes

### Component Architecture
#### [NEW] [SqueezePage.jsx](file:///Users/viveksuyal/Documents/Wishtune/frontend/src/pages/SqueezePage.jsx)
- **Hero**: "Manifestation without Homework".
- **Form**: Email input + "Get Free Song" button.
- **Social Proof**: "World's First Manifestation Music".

#### [NEW] [OTOPage.jsx](file:///Users/viveksuyal/Documents/Wishtune/frontend/src/pages/OTOPage.jsx)
